    <p>Given the HTML in the activecode below, add the appropriate CSS to style the h1 with a 28pt font, and rgb color consisting of red: 128, blue: 200, green: 99 and the <em>last</em> paragraph with a color of orange.</p>
    <listing>
    <program xml:id="q1_9" interactive="activecode" language="html" label="program-activecode-css-q1_9" include-source="yes">
      <input>
&lt;html&gt;
   &lt;body&gt;
      &lt;h1&gt;Learning about HTML&lt;/h1&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;HTML is a fun and easy language to learn&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Learning about CSS&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p class="css"&gt; CSS is fun too, but more challenging than HTML&lt;/p&gt;
   &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
        </input>
      <tests>


</tests>
